data.description: Nestled on a large lot, this well maintained home is conveniently located in a Boiling Springs neighborhood that has NO HOA! A handyman's dream workshop with peg board walls! As you arrive at the home the exterior curb appeal is eye catching, then you walk to the front porch to see the brick inlay that covers the floor of the rocking chair front porch. The great room has a large rock fireplace with gas logs. The Master bedroom has two (2) walk-in closets and a large walk-in shower that was recently updated. The home sports an oversized laundry room and large kitchen with an abundance of cabinets and great countertop space for preparing meals. The home has a breakfast area and a formal dining room. The outbuilding and carport do convey, and the roof is just a few months old.  Call today to schedule a private tour and see how this home can be your next address.
